WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.287
=Episode 9=

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.000
Miss Lu, you picked up drawing
and piano from a young age.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.160
Why are your fingers this coarse?

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:53.600
(I protect my fingers carefully
because of my piano practice.)

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.275
(I use a hand mask every day.)

00:02:03.525 --> 00:02:04.565
Morning, sis.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.960
What are you laughing at?

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.120
You don't remember?

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:12.080
Remember what?

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:14.600
Try thinking a bit harder.

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:19.200
Then tell me, what did I say

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.480
or what did I do?

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:23.560
You said you liked me.

00:02:24.120 --> 00:02:24.760
Impossible.

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:25.760
You even bit my hand.

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:28.440
- And you carried me back to my room.
- Ah, so you do remember?

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:32.920
Zhu,

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:35.000
where's the coffee you made for me?

00:02:37.320 --> 00:02:38.000
Dad.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:39.800
Hey, what are you doing?

00:02:39.937 --> 00:02:42.175
Wearing gloves while eating breakfast?

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:44.480
It's called a hand mask.

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:45.440
A hand mask?

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:47.720
Morning, Mr. Lu.

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:48.520
Morning.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:52.120
Mr. Lu, this project
is now fully formed.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:54.000
I'm bringing in my own team.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.520
Would you be able
to spare a few staff for me?

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.760
You handle it yourself, alright?

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:00.880
Regardless of the headcount,

00:03:00.880 --> 00:03:02.560
discuss it with
the HR department when the time comes.

00:03:02.570 --> 00:03:04.000
Consider it an opportunity to seize.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:04.800
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

00:03:09.875 --> 00:03:11.638
Sis, is it inconvenient with your hands?

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.360
Let me feed you.

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:20.280
Come on.

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:21.160
Open up.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:26.400
Come on.

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:27.720
Open up.

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:36.280
Zhu, look how old you are now.

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:37.360
Still letting your brother feed you?

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.600
Have you no shame?

00:03:43.320 --> 00:03:44.120
Have another bite.

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:46.960
Man.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:47.360
Yes?

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.760
Originally, this sci-tech
innovation project

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:53.200
was supposed to be given
to the Hangzhou branch.

00:03:53.275 --> 00:03:55.250
But we looked at your resume,

00:03:55.250 --> 00:03:58.320
and you really outshine
many experts in this field.

00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:00.720
So we're letting you
give it a try as a small test.

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:03.160
But this might be unfair to you.

00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:05.000
You'll have to stay
at the branch for a while.

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:08.520
However, the success
or failure of this project

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:11.360
will determine
if you can join the headquarters.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:13.720
It's fine, Mr. Lu.

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:14.760
You have already

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:17.280
given me so much help with this project.

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:18.200
Thank you very much.

00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:22.680
Zhu.

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:24.720
Your brother is here.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.600
I will treat him as my own.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:28.040
Don't you worry.

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:32.160
You guys carry on.

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:35.800
Hey, Zhu.

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.960
This hand mask is quite interesting.

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:40.960
Get a pair for me later too.

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:42.880
Okay.

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:50.800
Come on, let me keep feeding you.

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:54.400
No need, bro.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.240
This pile of documents is wrong.

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:04.600
Go and bring the ones from the back.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:05.400
Yes, boss.

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:21.360
Print out copies
of all these contracts later.

00:05:23.200 --> 00:05:24.200
Yes, boss.

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:36.120
What are you doing here?

00:05:38.840 --> 00:05:40.400
On the campus website,

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.200
I saw you were
recruiting an operations team.

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:43.600
So I caught a flight back home.

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:46.440
I think no one

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:49.120
is more suitable to be
your team leader than I am.

00:05:58.440 --> 00:05:59.960
Long time no see, Man.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.880
Long time no see, Lily.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:05.400
Fix this area up properly.

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:08.520
Wipe the glass over here a bit cleaner.

00:06:08.520 --> 00:06:10.960
Miss, this kind
of rough work isn't for you.

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:12.600
It's fine, I used to always...

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:17.280
I mean, my brother

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:18.320
just started.

00:06:18.320 --> 00:06:20.080
I want to give him a welcome gift.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:21.125
I'll do it myself.

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:30.560
Miss used to cherish her hands the most.

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:31.600
Why now...

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.400
This is still too dirty.

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:37.240
I'll go buy my brother
a potted plant instead.

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:38.360
I'll go wash my hands first.

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:40.100
Sure, I'll go get
the water ready for you.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:47.920
Enter.

00:06:59.200 --> 00:07:01.040
This gives it more life.

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:04.040
I still can't believe

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:06.680
that you, who needed
so much to stay in the US,

00:07:07.912 --> 00:07:09.792
would suddenly come back for my project.

00:07:12.080 --> 00:07:13.160
Do you remember back then,

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:18.080
you broke up with me
for the only spot in Grand One?

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:21.280
Coming back this time
is not like your style at all.

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:22.720
Yes.

00:07:23.837 --> 00:07:28.000
In the past, I could give up everything
for a spot and a green card.

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:30.260
But it wasn't until you left

00:07:30.270 --> 00:07:34.160
that I realized that you seem to be
more important than any of that.

00:07:40.287 --> 00:07:41.487
So my coming back this time

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:43.520
isn't just for the project.

00:07:45.320 --> 00:07:46.120
It's for you.

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:49.680
Man,

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:52.320
can we get back together?

00:08:01.090 --> 00:08:02.317
What kind of test is this now?

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:07.320
It seems you've already
developed traumatic syndrome.

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:10.000
I'm not a cat.

00:08:11.500 --> 00:08:13.300
How have your neck
and shoulders been lately?

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:18.160
I remember you used to
always have pain during projects.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.760
I'll just massage it for you.

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:42.680
Man.

00:08:50.520 --> 00:08:51.240
Zhu.

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:54.480
Why did you come to the office today?

00:08:57.760 --> 00:08:59.480
I'm helping my dad handle some business.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:02.880
Have you been crying?

00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:04.320
Who bullied you?

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.000
Do you have a car?

00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:19.320
It's at the entrance.

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:20.040
Let's go.

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:54.240
Zhu.

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:56.640
I'm here.

00:09:59.440 --> 00:10:00.240
Come on.

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:01.480
Let's go fly a kite.

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:03.640
Aren't I a bit old to be flying kites?

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:05.160
You go ahead and play.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.440
Fine.

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:09.360
Then I, Chen Tianze,
will brew you a coffee.

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:14.160
Here.

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:41.240
Look at how happy those kids are.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:43.240
I hope you can be as happy as they are.

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:55.960
Your barbecue is burnt.

00:11:13.662 --> 00:11:16.902
The food here is delicious. Try some.

00:11:19.280 --> 00:11:20.080
Ze,

00:11:21.800 --> 00:11:23.200
I don't have much of an appetite.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:26.600
If you have no appetite,
how can I eat alone?

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.840
You have so many people here.

00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:33.280
You come and eat together.

00:11:34.520 --> 00:11:36.937
No, they still have work to do.

00:11:36.975 --> 00:11:39.318
I am back this time
to handle so many things,

00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:42.012
and my dad specifically reminded me

00:11:42.012 --> 00:11:43.400
to keep a low profile.

00:11:43.800 --> 00:11:45.280
He isn't very well-liked in Hai City.

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:49.920
You call this keeping a low profile?

00:11:50.050 --> 00:11:51.410
Never mind that, just eat.

00:11:51.537 --> 00:11:52.497
It's my treat today.

00:12:07.125 --> 00:12:11.625
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:12:11.850 --> 00:12:15.638
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:12:15.813 --> 00:12:19.888
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:12:19.888 --> 00:12:24.025
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:12:24.150 --> 00:12:27.925
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:12:27.925 --> 00:12:31.700
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

00:12:31.700 --> 00:12:33.975
♪The you in my memories♪

00:12:33.975 --> 00:12:35.988
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:12:35.988 --> 00:12:41.425
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:12:42.988 --> 00:12:48.425
♪Forget you completely♪